description: Another boy from a small town wanted to move to Prague. He had big plans. His girlfriend and him would move to Prague, find good jobs, buy a flat, and eventually start a family. And to be honest, he had a pretty good shot at succeeding. Well, he made the first crucial step by visiting my office. I had a perfect position for someone like him. He used to work as a waiter so I offered him a nice and well-paid job at a luxury hotel. He was over the moon. I´m sure he was already thinking about the bright future ahead of him. Then I told him about the fee we charge. It took him completely by surprise. I hated shattering his dreams so I offered him an alternative way. He didn´t object much. When I offered him some extra cash, he even agreed to go a lot further. And I mean a lot...
title: Dirty Scout 115
